38
00:02:43,121 --> 00:02:45,621
- Look, I think...
- That I'm handling this.

39
00:02:46,499 --> 00:02:47,699
- Okay?
- But if you need me...

40
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:51,210
Yeah. What I need is for you
to stay out of my business.

41
