76
00:04:28,434 --> 00:04:30,314
Joey, are you crying?

77
00:04:30,395 --> 00:04:31,395
No.

78
00:04:32,772 --> 00:04:33,692
Oh...

79
00:04:33,773 --> 00:04:36,783
Stop crying before I start. Come on.

80
00:04:37,151 --> 00:04:39,651
Jeez. Oh, that's Jack. I gotta...

81
